_:b0__47984 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.50 75.10,51.60 75.10,51.60 42.40,11.50 42.40,11.50 75.10))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
