    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__7493.
_:b0__7493 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/author>;
