<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c2e2bf8072071d9d88150574dc84e15e>.
<#c2e2bf8072071d9d88150574dc84e15e> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/617>;
